{"tid":2047429,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北韓本月初全面復課","createTime":"2020-06-02T05:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T07:39:09.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a2aaeeb1660be4750ea7bf74962634d5b8bb794b","tid":2047429,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"北韓本月初全面復課<br />\n2020-06-02 HKT 13:39<br />\n<br />\n北韓的學校一般在4月1日展開新學期，但當局因應新型肺炎疫情延遲復課。報道稱，當地高中和大學已於4月20日復課，至於幼稚園、日間託兒中心等其他學校將於本月初復課，教師會嚴格遵守衛生規例，校方要預先消毒校園，並在所有課室及辦公室入口裝設體溫計和洗手液，學童將會接受病毒檢測，又建議家長預先教導子女注意防疫。<br />\n<br />\n根據北韓官方說法，當地未有出現新型肺炎確診病例，但南韓情報機構相信，北韓在一月底關閉邊境前，與中國仍有人員交流，不能排除當地爆發疫情。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529740-20200602.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529740-20200602.htm&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbcQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=6fd9c664\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529740-20200602.htm&h=0e18614f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529740-20200602.htm</a>"},{"pid":"11a399ace1d5e6ea6809f9de4129f7c8338650b0","tid":2047429,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/URfPLWi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FURfPLWi.jpg&h=b2b9ac8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/88185932_2001801003299503_1851875359847350272_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=eXVVdPPbLfUAX_Vpd6A&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=14&amp;oh=dd5be5c35c8f87081cff1fceb4fa3fa6&amp;oe=5EF9B7D2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F88185932_2001801003299503_1851875359847350272_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_sid%